HEADWORD: Pupillometer
<hw>Pu`pil*lom"e*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>pupilla</ets> pupil of the eye + <ets>-meter</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>An instrument for measuring the size of the
pupil of the pupil of the eye.</def>⟦br⟧
